gitCommit.subject: test(e2e): add comprehensive Playwright test suite and BUGS_FOUND.md
gitCommit.body:
test(e2e): add comprehensive Playwright test suite and BUGS_FOUND.md

- Introduce new e2e specifications covering error handling, mobile UI, page CRUD, settings, table operations, and workspace/organization flows.
- Add helper functions for user registration and workspace ID extraction used across all tests.
- Expand coverage to include navigation, API failure simulation, concurrent edits, markdown rendering, view mode toggles, and edge‑case interactions.
- Add BUGS_FOUND.md to document known issues uncovered by the new tests, providing context for future fixes.

gitCommit.subject: test(e2e): add comprehensive Playwright test suite and BUGS_FOUND.md
gitCommit.body:
test(e2e): add comprehensive Playwright test suite and BUGS_FOUND.md

- Introduce new e2e specifications covering error handling, mobile UI, page CRUD, settings, table operations, and workspace/organization flows.
- Add helper functions for user registration and workspace ID extraction used across all tests.
- Expand coverage to include navigation, API failure simulation, concurrent edits, markdown rendering, view mode toggles, and edge‑case interactions.
- Add BUGS_FOUND.md to document known issues uncovered by the new tests, providing context for future fixes.
